*"Njegova *odluka* da ode bila je neočekivana." (His decision to leave was unexpected.)

*"Njen *odlučan* stav donela je mir u porodicu." (Her resolute stance brought peace to the family.)

*"Mnogi su bili zadovoljni *odlukom* da se preselimo." (Many were pleased with the decision to move.)

*"U njegovoj *odluci* nije bilo mesta za kompromis." (There was no room for compromise in his decision.)

*"Njena *odlučnost* bila je impresivna." (Her determination was impressive.)